We can explore unknown systems by sending Longprobe Y-wing units on Reconnaissance missions to those locations.  We can also make use of our capital ships for exploration; these ships risk destruction, however, should they encounter an Imperial fleet.  If we should locate an unpopulated system through the course of our exploration, we can send a regiment of troopers via ship to establish a base there.  Building facilities on that system will bring colonists who will provide a very loyal population base.  Longprobe Y-wings are considered special forces and can be accessed through their system's Defenses window. 